works.description: For the lovers of fine watchmaking, German firm Timekeeper Chronometrie has come up with the new “Mystery of Time” clock, which is sure to become the conversation piece of your living room. The limited edition Mystery of Time Trible Axes Tourbillon with Planetary was in the making for a long 10 years, and only 12 copies have been produced. An upshot of the imagination Tilmann von dem Knesebeck, the Timekeeper Chronometrie stands for reunion of historical movements with high quality cases.
